The ghost's eyes light up as you hold out the chewed-up cartridge. For the first time, his face breaks into a smile.  "you found it! i thought it was lost forever!"  The ghost reaches out a spectral hand to take the cartridge, silvery tears leaking down his face. "i can finally wake up now. i can finally go back to the real house."

Clutching the cartridge to his chest, the sniffling ghost mouths a silent "thank you, prickles" and fades out of view, leaving you alone.

Prickles. That's right. That's your name.
